{"tid":940761,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【年度聖誕歌】看 看著你的臉 播著薄格片 毒癮在膀胱蔓延","createTime":"2018-12-14T07:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T07:14:04.000Z","uid":45331,"like":171,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5fb712fb437ef67c09e00663d0e5098a0a16c72f","tid":940761,"uid":45331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T07:52:27.000Z","msg":"看 看著你的臉 播著薄格片<br />\n毒癮在膀胱蔓延<br />\n我 快射到痴線 五十個缺點<br />\n滿面濃瘡彷彿給我加冕<br />\n<br />\n不管燈飾多普遍 得我電視幕前<br />\n一聲不發拔出寶劍<br />\n<br />\n今晚我注定手淫 我太毒尚有抱枕<br />\n一分鐘發射可能 聖誕我是種遺憾<br />\n簡單一碌棍 手心的抖震<br />\n示意我看AV不需紙巾<br />\n收卡說「你是好人」 永遠沒性的光棍<br />\n再回望這生 哪有女陪襯<br />\n一個勿呻吟 搵外快情人 不想單身<br />\n<br />\n從來不相信一生不愛侶 遺留雙手一對<br />\n別再等 別再等 但我的積蓄得幾百蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d94940f6390ab4d80f61a6d86f577d277d9bdda","tid":940761,"uid":45331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T07:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744cffaf98fe89bf9510c00c48076ded55b2d699","tid":940761,"uid":201892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T08:06:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"19cad855ad6dbf4ed44ba19330f7f29c1d248720","tid":940761,"uid":160794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T08:19:21.000Z","msg":"唱出心聲"},{"pid":"77eb65bcd102049467dac3ecf98092a3456b02fd","tid":940761,"uid":45331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T08:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c132b43f7fa6a77dcf03897991b3031a72b529fe","tid":940761,"uid":45331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T08:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d76a95bedb6d74db1f387e8d0c7ca6b007f3a1","tid":940761,"uid":208159,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"re